<materialsCitation id="4B863CC48F343E40F7DFF330F720F761" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3802853315" pageId="6" pageNumber="378">“Mata Taua, Usina Trapiche, municipality of Sirinhaém, state of Pernambuco, Brazil, 8° 33’ 46-13” 8, 35° 10° 9-09” W, ¢l- evation 85 m.”</materialsCitation>
